description:
The dazzling Jenna Dewan Tatum (Step up, Supergirl) stops by Anna’s house in this lively episode! Jenna shares her favorite show to binge-watch and how she fights off assailants in her dreams. Anna, Jenna, and Sim also dish about Channing Tatum and Chris Pratt’s bromance, getting recognized at the grocery store and Anna’s brilliant performance in Just Friends. Jenna also teaches Anna a few dance moves—with stripper shoes on! (Check out the video on our Facebook and Twitter!) The gang then gives unqualified advice to a woman with concerns about dating “casually,” and tries to help a bride-to-be decide whether her passion for cats is a relationship deal-breaker. 

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
